OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late brightness.
OL,7,FThen outbreaks of rain will spread
OL,8,Fnortheast for a time overnight before
OL,9,Fit turns drier later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FQuite cloudy in the morning
OL,12,Fwith some rain. Variable amounts of
OL,13,Fcloud and sunny spells in the
OL,14,Fafternoon along with scattered slow
OL,15,Fmoving showers, occasionally heavy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
